Also Download Metadata table for Attribute Definition: http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/node/270 The ACS and 2010 Census data by Tract can be linked using the geoid field, to the GEOID10 field in the TRACTS_2010 Dataset :http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/content/tracts-census-2010  NOTE:  When importing the .csv files into a Database,  the software may try to turn the geoid field into a number field, which will drop the first 0 from the census code and will make the table not linkable to the geographies.
